    "summary": {
      "value": "Shadow Strike reduces MP and causes action loss with swords."
    },
    "description": "<blockquote><p><span style=\"font-family:'EB Garamond', sans-serif\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">Requirements: </strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">you must have mastered one or more Classes among </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>Darkblade</strong> </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">and </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>Esper</strong>.</span></p></blockquote><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">When you hit one or more creatures with an attack from your </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>Shadow Strike</strong> </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Skill using a weapon that belongs to the </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>sword</strong> </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Category, each of those creatures loses an amount of Mind Points equal to </span><span class=\"fontstyle3\"><strong>【</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>the number you rolled on your Might die for Shadow Strike</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle3\"><strong>】</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">. Then, if </span><span class=\"fontstyle3\"><strong>【</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>the number you rolled on your Might die for Shadow Strike</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle3\"><strong>】 </strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>was 8 or higher</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">, you may choose one creature hit by the attack: if that creature is your </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>focus</strong> </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">or you have a </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>Bond</strong> </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">towards them, that creature will perform one fewer action during their next turn (to a minimum of zero actions).</span></p>",
